Class ChannelAdminService

java.lang.Object
com.powerbi.api.service.ChannelAdminService
@Service public class ChannelAdminService extends Object
Service class responsible for managing ChannelAdmin entities. Handles operations related to retrieving, adding, and removing channel admins, along with authorization checks to ensure proper access control.
